 ceilings, was meticulously restored through a unique sandblasting process with walnut shells, preserving the wood’s natural texture while harmonizing with new floors. This thoughtful treatment emphasizes the continuity between the cabin’s past and its revitalized design.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562471\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562471\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-4-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A cozy living room with a beige sectional sofa, round marble coffee table, and a floor lamp. Decor includes throw pillows, a fur rug, candles, and houseplants. Large windows provide natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-4-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-4-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-4-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-4-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562472\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562472\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-5-810x810.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden vaulted ceiling with exposed beams and triangular windows reflecting trees.\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-5-810x810.jpg