n-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-9-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with white cabinets and minimalist decor, featuring a large window view of a snow-covered landscape with trees.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-9-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-9-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-9-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562477\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562477\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-10-810x456.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with sleek gray cabinets, built-in appliances, and light wood flooring. A small decorative clock is mounted on the wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"456\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-10-810x456.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-10-800x450.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-10-768x432.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-10-600x337.jpg 600w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562478\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562478\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-11-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A cozy attic room with a sloped wooden ceiling features a sofa, a wooden coffee table, a guitar, and large triangular windows overlooking green trees. A small red lamp sits on the table.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-11-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-11-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eUp in the loft, oversized windows provide unobstructed views of the treetops, reinforcing the cabin’s integration with the landscape. Here, bespoke built-in cabinetry displays vintage records and a turntable, celebrating the cabin’s mid-century charm. Adding a touch of whimsy, a Noguchi Akari lantern placed in the corner, illuminates the space in soft light.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562479\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562479\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-12-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Cozy room with a large window revealing a forest view, a fluffy chair, a layered paper lamp on the floor, and a potted plant on a ledge under a slanted wooden ceiling.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-12-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-12-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-12-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-12-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562480\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562480\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-13-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A colorful acoustic guitar on a stand in a cozy attic room, with a lamp, speaker, and books nearby. A modern mobile hangs from the ceiling near a window.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-13-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-13-800x1066.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-13-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-13-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562481\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562481\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-14-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A cozy attic room with slanted wooden ceiling, featuring shelves with books, a colorful guitar, speakers, and decorative items.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-14-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-14-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562482\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562482\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-15-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Entryway with a dark wall, coat hooks, a brown jacket, and a red bag hanging. A plant and a bench are nearby. A map of Tel Aviv is framed on the wall. A doorway leads to a bright room.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-15-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-15-800x1066.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-15-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-15-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562483\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562483\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-16-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A neatly made bed with beige pillows and white bedding, flanked by two wooden nightstands with green lamps. Beige curtains cover the wall behind the bed.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-16-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-16-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe sleeping areas are designed as intimate retreats, each outfitted with Scandinavian-inspired decor, plush rugs, and soft fabrics. The main bedroom is particularly striking with its vintage-inspired reading nook accented in Irish Green, matched with a plush velvet sofa, creating an inviting spot to unwind. Thoughtful lighting fixtures, including wall sconces and floor lamps, add a gentle, ambient glow that enhances the overall sense of calm.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562484\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562484\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-17-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A cozy bedroom with a bed in the foreground, a dark sofa against a green wall, a framed picture above, and a small lamp on a side table.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-17-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-17-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-17-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562485\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562485\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-18-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern, organized closet with white shelving, hanging clothes, a full-length mirror, plants, and wall art on a beige paneled wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-18-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-18-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-18-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562486\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562486\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-19-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A tidy bedroom with a white bed, freestanding mirror, and wall art. A wooden nightstand holds a lamp. Artwork is reflected in the mirror.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-19-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-19-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-19-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562487\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562487\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-20-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A snow-covered wooden deck with a red rocking chair. Large trees and the sun are visible in the background next to a black house with large windows.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-20-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-20-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-20-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-20-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562488\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562488\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-21-810x1135.jpg\" alt=\"A cabin surrounded by snow-covered trees with a parked vehicle nearby during winter.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1135\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-21-810x1135.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-21-800x1121.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-21-768x1076.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-21-1097x1536.jpg 1097w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562489\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562489\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-22-810x539.jpg\" alt=\"Aerial view of a snow-covered cabin surrounded by tall pine trees in a forest.\" width=\"810\" height=\"539\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-22-810x539.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-22-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-22-768x511.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architecture-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=562490\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-562490\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Arrowhead-Double-A-Frame-House-Dan-Brunn-Architectur